{"tid":1825081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[ 就 2020年1月14日 西九龍中心8樓美食廣場有一名男子被便衣警員帶走事宜]","createTime":"2020-01-15T03:34:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T17:44:45.000Z","uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c36331481925db7911d224af298d30f94cb96ddd","tid":1825081,"uid":244704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T03:34:20.000Z","msg":"[ 就 2020年1月14日 西九龍中心8樓美食廣場有一名男子被便衣警員帶走事宜] <br />\n<br />\n對於有便衣警員於昨午在本中心截查並帶走一名男子事件 ，管理處非常關注，並已即時去函深水埗分區警署作了解，現待警署回覆。<br />\n<br />\n管理處重申，基本上在不影響途人安全情況下，本中心範圍內可進行拍照。但如拍攝者會將拍攝內容作公開播放，均須事前向管理處申請。 <br />\n<br />\n就有關情況，管理處已加派保安巡邏，另如租戶需要任何協助，請與本中心管理處聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109324349107600/posts/3565970853442915/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109324349107600%2Fposts%2F3565970853442915%2F&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=a274536f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109324349107600/posts/3565970853442915/</a>"},{"pid":"5bfa6fc5e6c6321840b38a9b748c17cb88c0ba0a","tid":1825081,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-15T17:44:45.000Z","msg":"( please forward to your English reading friends, colleagues, etc) <br />\n<br />\nMan arrested after taking picture of Hong Kong police in restaurant, with councillor decrying incident as &lsquo;arbitrary arrest&rsquo; | South China Morning Post<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fhong-kong%2Flaw-and-crime%2Farticle%2F3046100%2Fman-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera&d=8FzWv2H1QRiLw4sTAqHlBg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=182c166f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/law-and-crime/article/3046100/man-arrested-after-catching-hong-kong-police-camera</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\